    org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class EventStream
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
    Steam of Events to be processed by the CEPEngine.

    The EventStream leverages the notification mechanism of EMF, therefore it is an extension to the EObjectImpl type.
